# audience-data-models

## Fan Profile Data Structure

Importance Score: 95/100

Core data models for managing fan profiles across music platforms:

```typescript
interface FanProfile {
  // Cross-platform music identity
  platformIds: {
    spotify?: string
    lastfm?: string
    soundcloud?: string
  }
  // Genre affinity scoring
  genreAffinities: {
    [genre: string]: {
      score: number // 0-100
      confidence: number // 0-1
      lastUpdated: Date
    }
  }
  // Artist relationship mapping  
  artistFollowing: {
    artistId: string
    platform: string
    engagementLevel: 'casual' | 'engaged' | 'superfan'
    firstSeen: Date
  }[]
}
```

